Match Day 4 of the Premier League continues on Sunday. There will be only two matches, as most of the games were played yesterday. First, Everton welcome Wolverhampton Wanderers to Goodison Park. The last fixture for this week, is the North London Derby at the Emirates between Arsenal and Tottenham. Sunday, September 1
